# .dockerignore — files excluded from the Docker build context
#
# When you run `docker build`, Docker sends all files in the directory
# to the Docker daemon (the "build context"). Large or unnecessary files
# slow down the build and increase image size.
# .dockerignore works like .gitignore — patterns here are excluded.

.git
.github
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
tests/
*.md
.dockerignore
